01:10:05,220 --> 01:10:07,660
 da li snaga može biti

925
01:10:07,660 --> 01:10:08,120
 ne znam,

926
01:10:08,120 --> 01:10:10,140
 u pozadina

927
01:10:10,140 --> 01:10:11,620
 virtualnog novca

928
01:10:11,620 --> 01:10:12,180
 temeljenog

929
01:10:12,180 --> 01:10:12,940
 na recimo

930
01:10:12,940 --> 01:10:14,180
 nekoj kršćanskoj valuti

931
01:10:14,180 --> 01:10:15,020
 recimo

932
01:10:15,020 --> 01:10:15,400
 neka

933
