 Ne mora biti

947
01:10:33,140 --> 01:10:33,820
 stvarni novac

948
01:10:33,820 --> 01:10:34,900
 kao primjer svijetu,

949
01:10:34,900 --> 01:10:36,320
 neke bolje ekonomije.

950
01:10:36,320 --> 01:10:37,900
 Možda malo lupa,

951
01:10:37,900 --> 01:10:39,440
 malo mislim da se na neki način

952
01:10:39,440 --> 01:10:41,480
 među svojim kolegicama

953
01:10:41,480 --> 01:10:42,160
 i kolegama,

954
01:10:42,160 --> 01:10:43,480
 pa mi oprostite.

955
01:10:43,480 --> 01:10:44,920
 Ako možete kratko reći?

956
01:10:44,920 --> 01:10:46,940
 Evo,

957
01:10:46,940 --> 01:10:48,840
 vrlo kratko.

958
01:10:48,840 --> 01:10:49,180
 Znači,

959
01:10:49,180 --> 01:10:50,360
 što se tiče,

960
01:10:50,360 --> 01:10:52,640
 prepostajem da u tom pravcu

961
01:10:52,640 --> 01:10:53,400
 ide pitanje

962
01:10:53,400 --> 01:10:54,880
 konkretizacije,

963
01:10:54,880 --> 01:10:56,600
 odnosno na neki način

964
01:10:56,600 --> 01:10:58,100
 primjene ovih

965
01:10:58,100 --> 01:10:59,720
 principa u praksi

966
01:10:59,720 --> 01:11:00,980
 i na neki način,

967
01:11:00,980 --> 01:11:02,300
 ako sam dobro razumio,

968
01:11:02,300 --> 01:11:04,740
 da li postoji platforma

969
01:11:04,740 --> 01:11:06,140
 na koji ćemo mi jedni druga

970
01:11:06,140 --> 01:11:06,720
 prepoznati.

971
01:11:06,720 --> 01:11:09,140
 Kao da postoji,

972
01:11:09,140 --> 01:11:10,360
 kao da bismo razvili

973
01:11:10,360 --> 01:11:11,500
 nekakvu etiketu,

974
01:11:11,500 --> 01:11:12,560
 nekakav,

975
01:11:12,560 --> 01:11:13,180
 rekli bismo,

976
01:11:13,180 --> 01:11:13,660
 label,

977
01:11:13,660 --> 01:11:14,680
 koji bi onda stavili

978
01:11:14,680 --> 01:11:15,460
 na svoj proizvod

979
01:11:15,460 --> 01:11:16,220
 i na svoju uslugu,

980
01:11:16,220 --> 01:11:17,300
 pa bi onda mi jedni druga

981
